        Constructor.
        Parameters:
        id - ID.
        textureRegion - TextureRegion.
        xOffset - Offset in the X axis in pixels that should be applied when rendering this character.
        yOffset - Offset in the Y axis in pixels that should be applied when rendering this character.
        xAdvance - Offset in the X axis in pixels that should be applied when rendering the next character after this one.
        channel - Color channel of the letter in the texture. Use CHANNEL_R, CHANNEL_G, CHANNEL_B, CHANNEL_A, or CHANNEL_RGBA.
